@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}
<br/>
<div style="background-color: #313131; color: #FFFFFF; padding: 40px; border-radius: 10px; max-width: 800px; margin: auto;">
    <h1 style="color: #5eedab; text-align: center;">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Welcome to ABC Retail, your number one source for all things fashion. We're dedicated to giving you the very best of clothing, with a focus on quality, customer service, and uniqueness.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Founded in 2024, ABC Retail has come a long way from its beginnings. When we first started out, our passion for "style that speaks" drove us to quit our day jobs, do tons of research, and turn hard work and inspiration into a booming online store. We now serve customers all over the world and are thrilled to be a part of the fashion industry.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6;">
        We hope you enjoy our products as much as we enjoy offering them to you. If you have any questions or comments, please don't hesitate to contact us.
    </p>

   
</div>
